reviewText: I got these SO long ago and never wrote a review. I remember they got to me fast, and in perfect condition. I really got into the anime, when I bought them and almost watched the DVD's everyday. Fun fact, I met Masashi Kishimoto fact-to-face and spoke with him at the NYC comic con. I got his autograph and put it right next to the DVD's I got on here, since they are the first official Naruto items I ever bought/owned.
